    //Mail
    "blue704.JojaCC_FarmerBundleBookCaskMail.text": "Dear @,^^Again I would just like to thank you for all of the work that you did completing the Farmer Bundle. Thanks to you I can spend some time cooking for the community and sharing the recipes that have been passed down to me from my mother.^^But I have one more small present for you. Mr. Todd said that he was going to build that cellar in the pantry for us and I thought that you might need a few casks to help get you started? These have been gathering dust in our house so I wanted you to have them. Please come my new shop when you have the chance!^^Love, Evelyn",
